    "updated_at": "2017-02-23T21:44:14Z",
    "body": "Thank you for replying!\r\n\r\nI'm assuming this is a hard-coded value and can't be changed after Electron is built. Could this be made configurable? Allowing app authors to adjust the default max memory would be very useful. How costly would such a change be?\r\n\r\nI also just noticed there is an `app.commandLine.appendSwitch` API. I don't suppose that would work for increasing available memory, would it?"
